This Grails plugin allows you to convert texts using XWiki Rendering Framework.

{code:java}
class SomeController {

    def xwikiRenderer

    def someAction = {
        String testString = """
        =level1=
        **bold**
        """
        String result = xwikiRenderer.render(textString)
        ...
    }

}
{code}

See "XWiki Rendering Framework":http://rendering.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Main/WebHome for the details about the framework.
